    <abstract>
      <t>A Layer 2 Gateway (L2GW) is used for interconnecting a Layer 2
   overlay network [NVO3FRWK] and a Layer 2 bridged network [IEEE802.1Q]
   to form a single Layer 2 virtual network.  This draft describes data
   plane interconnection and control plane interworking at the L2GW.</t>
    </abstract>
